<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        h1, h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1><%= title %></h1>

    <p>To delete your data from our application, please follow these steps:</p>

    <h2>Option 1: Through Your Account</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Log in to your account at <a href="https://www.nhatrangseafood.com">https://www.nhatrangseafood.com</a></li>
        <li>Go to your Account Settings</li>
        <li>Click on the "Delete My Data" button</li>
        <li>Confirm your decision</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Option 2: Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you're unable to access your account or prefer to have us handle the data deletion process, please:</p>
    <ol>
        <li>Send an email to <a href="mailto:privacy@nhatrangseafood.com">privacy@nhatrangseafood.com</a></li>
        <li>Use the subject line "Data Deletion Request"</li>
        <li>Include in your email:
            <ul>
                <li>Your full name</li>
                <li>The email address associated with your account</li>
                <li>A clear statement that you want your data deleted</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ol>

    <h2>What Happens Next</h2>
    <p>Once we receive your request, we will:
        <ol>
            <li>Verify your identity</li>
            <li>Process your data deletion request within 30 days</li>
            <li>Send you a confirmation email once your data has been deleted</li>
        </ol>
    </p>

    <h2>Questions?</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about the data deletion process, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@nhatrangseafood.com">privacy@nhatrangseafood.com</a>.</p>
</body>
</html>
